485
00:39:57,268 --> 00:39:58,565
Tommy!

486
00:39:58,769 --> 00:40:02,261
Por favor, eu quero ajudar ele.

487
00:40:09,747 --> 00:40:12,580
- Tire isso daqui.
- Certo.

488
00:40:14,418 --> 00:40:15,715
Vai ficar bem.

489
00:40:15,920 --> 00:40:19,447
